  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      113.34,
      506.49,
      143.95
    ],
    "text": "Organized Criminal Arrested Overseas and Repatriated by Air \u2013 Criminal Investigation Department",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      158.41,
      508.97,
      199.29
    ],
    "text": "A suspect involved in organized crime and narcotics trafficking in Sri Lanka has been arrested through a coordinated international operation conducted with the assistance of the State Intelligence Service and the State Security Service of Azerbaijan.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      213.73,
      506.27,
      254.64
    ],
    "text": "The suspect was repatriated to Sri Lanka on 10 May 2026 by a team of officers from the Criminal Investigation Department and subsequently handed over to the Colombo Crimes Division for further investigations.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      269.2,
      300.41,
      282.48
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 48-year-old resident of Ja-Ela.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      324.93,
      202.64,
      339.94
    ],
    "text": "Investigative Findings",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      354.28,
      508.79,
      408.96
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the suspect maintained close links with organized criminal networks and drug traffickers, including Ganemulla Sanjeewa, Kehelbaddara Padme, and Commando Salintha, and was actively involved in coordinating illicit drug trafficking operations.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      423.54,
      407.35,
      436.82
    ],
    "text": "Further details revealed through investigations include the following:",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      451.38,
      523.71,
      644.09
    ],
    "text": "\u2022 On 06 December 2020, Excise officers arrested four suspects along with four vehicles transporting 100 kilograms of heroin and 100 kilograms of crystal methamphetamine (\u201cIce\u201d). Investigations indicate that the suspect orchestrated the smuggling operation from abroad, directing traffickers based in Dubai. \u2022 On 31 December 2023, the suspect is alleged to have directed the assassination of an individual within the Grandpass Police Division, linked to disputes arising from drug trafficking activities. \u2022 On 25 July 2024, investigations have revealed that the suspect directed another shooting incident in which a woman and a three-wheeler driver involved in drug trafficking were killed within the Grandpass Police Division. \u2022 On 13 December 2024, it has been established that followers acting under the suspect\u2019s direction carried out a shooting incident and caused damage to a residence belonging to an organized criminal located at Veediya Mawatha, Kandana, within the Kandana Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "SymbolMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.960000038146973,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      658.53,
      511.12,
      685.61
    ],
    "text": "A 72-hour detention order has been obtained against the suspect, and further investigations are being conducted by the Colombo Crimes Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  }
]